cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image and video processing. The use of CNN-based models also suggests a Machine Learning (cs.MM) sub-category. The study of temporal consistency between consecutive video frames indicates a possible sub-category of Learning (cs.LG). The use of object detection models suggests an Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the study of structure options and fusion strategies may also fall under the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
